de.griefed.serverpackcreator

Class VersionLister

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.griefed.serverpackcreator.VersionLister

  • @Component
public class VersionLister
extends java.lang.Object
    Create lists of versions for Minecraft, Fabric and Forge. Provides getters for retrieving Minecraft and Fabric version lists and getForgeVersionsList(String) to retrieve a list of available Forge versions for a given Minecraft version. Instantiating this class automatically creates the Minecraft and Fabric lists, for immediate access through getMinecraftReleaseVersions() and getFabricVersions() respectively. Also provides getters for retrieving the latest or release versions of Fabric.
